title: Buffalo Girls
description:
Movie Description
A rollicking, fictionalized account of the life of Martha Jane Canary, better known as Calamity Jane, as she cuts a wide swath through the Old West. Based on Larry McMurtry&#039;s novel, this story also features Buffalo Bill, Annie Oakley, Sitting Bull and other Western legends. Recipient of ten Emmy nominations.

Credits 
Cast: Melanie Griffith 
Director: Rod Hardy 

Synopsis
Television adaptation of Larry McMurtry&#039;s novel about famous frontierswoman Calamity Jane, who learned to cope -- and even triumph -- in the predominantly male world of the 1870&#039;s west.
